text: Kelli McMullen-Temple (born 25 October 1960) is a Canadian equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Columbus, Ohio
